"Police have issued a warrant
for the arrest of Mildred Kemp, age 1 9,

01:00:48.945 --> 01:00:53.211
"who had been employed as the
Wright children's nanny since August."

01:00:53.282 --> 01:00:56.911
-Mildred Kemp?
-Holy shit. Listen to this.

01:00:57.020 --> 01:00:58.783
"According to sources
close to the family,

01:00:58.821 --> 01:01:01.688
"Kemp had became romantically
obsessed with Dr. Wright

01:01:01.758 --> 01:01:05.421
"since his wife's death
in a car accident last February.

01:01:05.495 --> 01:01:08.760
"Despite police efforts,
Kemp remains at large."

01:01:08.831 --> 01:01:10.355
Wait, what...

01:01:11.834 --> 01:01:14.962
Look. Look what she's wearing.

01:01:17.140 --> 01:01:19.335
The pearls.

01:01:19.409 --> 01:01:22.708
Rachel said they were a gift
from an old patient.

01:01:22.779 --> 01:01:26.977
She put them around my neck.
Like... Like she was proud of them.

01:01:28.985 --> 01:01:31.351
Yeah, well, lucky for us,
now we have proof.

01:01:32.255 --> 01:01:35.281
Yeah, if we can get our hands on them.

01:01:36.259 --> 01:01:39.990
Don't worry about that.
This ends tonight.

01:02:16.632 --> 01:02:18.122
Shit.

01:02:20.436 --> 01:02:21.767
Hey, look.

01:02:33.549 --> 01:02:36.416
-Alex, where are you going?
-Just go downstairs and get her keys.

01:02:36.486 --> 01:02:39.717
-What are you gonna do?
-Just get her keys.

01:03:46.789 --> 01:03:49.223
What are you looking for, Anna?

01:03:50.059 --> 01:03:52.789
Is it these? Are you looking for these?

01:03:56.165 --> 01:03:57.928
You should take them.

01:03:58.901 --> 01:04:01.199
Please. They mean nothing to me.

01:04:03.139 --> 01:04:05.039
We know, Rachel.

01:04:06.742 --> 01:04:08.733
We know everything.

01:04:11.948 --> 01:04:13.540
You caught me.

01:04:16.018 --> 01:04:17.110
Here.

01:04:23.059 --> 01:04:24.390
Alex!

01:04:26.162 --> 01:04:27.356
Alex!

01:04:54.457 --> 01:04:55.549
Anna.

01:04:57.059 --> 01:04:59.220
I don't want to hurt you.

01:05:00.763 --> 01:05:03.231
This isn't how I wanted it.

01:05:04.267 --> 01:05:06.701
You can make this easy.

01:05:17.013 --> 01:05:19.072
-Anna.
-Alex.

01:05:22.218 --> 01:05:26.416
-What happened?
-She drugged me. She drugged me.

01:05:26.489 --> 01:05:28.150
Anna? Open the door.

01:05:28.224 --> 01:05:30.658
Anna, listen to me.

01:05:30.726 --> 01:05:34.457
-You have to get that necklace.
-I did. I got it.

01:05:34.897 --> 01:05:37.525
Anna! Open this goddamn door!

01:05:42.972 --> 01:05:44.906
You gotta go to Emery, okay?

01:05:44.974 --> 01:05:47.807
-No. No.
-Yes. He'll believe you.

01:05:47.877 --> 01:05:50.072
-Anna!
-I can't leave you here.

01:05:51.514 --> 01:05:53.345
Pinkie pact.

01:05:54.050 --> 01:05:55.244
Anna!

01:05:55.318 --> 01:05:58.549
-Okay.
-Okay.

01:06:00.389 --> 01:06:02.050
I love you.

01:06:12.535 --> 01:06:15.402
I'll come back for you, okay? I promise.

01:06:41.797 --> 01:06:43.025
Anna!

01:06:58.280 --> 01:07:01.249
So, you're alleging that
Miss Summers is actually a woman

01:07:01.317 --> 01:07:02.807
-named Mildred Kemp?
-Yes.

01:07:02.885 --> 01:07:05.581
And she was the one responsible
for the fire?

01:07:05.654 --> 01:07:07.281
That's right. It wasn't an accident.

01:07:07.356 --> 01:07:10.519
She murdered our mother,
and now she's after us.

01:07:11.594 --> 01:07:17.089
-Listen, I know how this sounds, but...
-No. Mildred Kemp. I remember her.

01:07:18.667 --> 01:07:22.262
Out west in Woolridge County,
years ago, wife died,

01:07:22.338 --> 01:07:25.102
man hired some nanny
who killed all the children.

01:07:25.174 --> 01:07:27.335
That's right, but they never caught her.

01:07:27.410 --> 01:07:31.904
Okay, listen, Mrs. Wright
had a pearl necklace, three strands.

01:07:31.981 --> 01:07:34.415
There are pictures of it
on the lnternet if you wanna see.

01:07:34.483 --> 01:07:35.973
And?

01:07:40.823 --> 01:07:43.087
Rachel is Mildred Kemp.

01:07:43.159 --> 01:07:45.787
Okay? She's trying to kill us
and marry our father,

01:07:45.861 --> 01:07:47.886
just like she did to them.

01:07:53.035 --> 01:07:55.731
Listen, I want you to sit tight.

01:07:55.805 --> 01:07:57.932
Jerry is right outside that door.

01:07:58.040 --> 01:07:59.905
I'm gonna pull up Miss Summers
on the system.

01:07:59.942 --> 01:08:02.740
No, there's no time for that.
You have to go to my house.

01:08:02.812 --> 01:08:07.146
Alex is still there, and I'm afraid
something's gonna happen to her.

